Funding Support and Contact
</div>

The <i>Medicago truncatula</i> Gene Expression Atlas project is supported
by the National Research Initiative (NRI)
Plant Genome Program of the USDA Cooperative State Research, Education
and Extension Service (CSREES).
<br /><br />

For overall questions and collaboration opportunities regarding the MtGEA project, please contact the
principle investigator of the project,
